To Do:

Step 1: Click Azure Active Directory
Step 2: Click Users
Step 3: Click New User at the top left and "Create new user" or "Invite external user"
Step 4: Fill in the Basics, Properties, Assignments & Review + create information
Step 5: You can use the auto-generated password or the user can create their own
Step 6: Once everything has been filled out just hit create at the bottom
